Insomnito|™ is a blend of botanicals, nutrients and neurotransmitter precursors designed to support quality, restful sleep. By providing nutritional support for calm mental function, Insomnitol™ supports the body’s natural ability to fall and stay asleep. Key ingredients include botanicals that support nervous system function, PharmaGABA® (a patented form of gamma-aminobutyric acid (GABA)), L-theanine, melatonin, 5-hydroxytryptophan (5-HTP) and pyridoxal-5-phosphate (an activated form of vitamin B6).
